166
00:18:34,213 --> 00:18:36,613
You got a flat ass anyway!

167
00:18:37,049 --> 00:18:38,914
Vamos, chico, vamos!

168
00:18:38,951 --> 00:18:41,351
You'll see him tomorrow.

169
00:18:41,386 --> 00:18:43,286
Get out!

170
00:18:49,862 --> 00:18:51,489
Estúpido!

171
00:18:54,933 --> 00:18:57,766
...last Saturday night
I made 100 pesos

172
00:18:57,803 --> 00:19:00,601
for letting 10 members
of the National Ballet

173
00:19:00,639 --> 00:19:01,833
suck me off.

174
00:19:03,008 --> 00:19:05,033
