175
00:19:05,077 --> 00:19:07,272
If you do it for money,
you're not a fag.

176
00:19:43,582 --> 00:19:45,880
You know him?

177
00:19:45,918 --> 00:19:46,907
No.

178
00:19:52,724 --> 00:19:53,691
Hello.

179
00:19:53,725 --> 00:19:55,090
I'm sorry about the other day.

180
00:19:55,127 --> 00:19:56,185
No, don't worry.
Forget it.

181
00:19:56,228 --> 00:19:58,219
- I am Reinaldo.
- I am Pepe.

182
00:19:58,263 --> 00:20:00,254
- How about some ice cream?
- Yes!

183
00:20:00,299 --> 00:20:02,324
Today they have only vanilla.

184
00:20:03,368 --> 00:20:06,565
Bring him a banana split
with pistacho.

185
00:20:06,605 --> 00:20:08,368
One ice cream!

186
00:20:08,941 --> 00:20:09,703
Go.

187
00:20:10,709 --> 00:20:13,507
So where you from,
Reinaldo?

188
00:20:13,545 --> 00:20:15,706
I am a guajiro,
from Oriente.

189
00:20:15,747 --> 00:20:17,715
- Does it matter where I'm from?
- No.

190
00:20:17,749 --> 00:20:19,148
What do you do?

191
00:20:19,218 --> 00:20:21,948
I just got a job now
in the National Library,

192
00:20:21,987 --> 00:20:24,649
but I would like to be
a writer.

193
00:20:26,391 --> 00:20:29,053
You poor thing.

194
00:20:29,094 --> 00:20:31,619
A country boy in Havana
to serve the Revolution.

195
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:50,946
- Where's your mother?
- En la bodega.

196
00:20:50,983 --> 00:20:52,883
Give me the key.

197
00:20:52,918 --> 00:20:54,647
Chau.

198
00:20:54,686 --> 00:20:55,618
Vamos!

199
00:21:10,736 --> 00:21:12,727
She says it works,

200
00:21:12,771 --> 00:21:14,932
just one key is a little off.

201
00:21:14,973 --> 00:21:17,168
How can I thank you?

202
00:21:21,713 --> 00:21:23,044
What are you doing?

203
00:21:23,081 --> 00:21:24,412
