on the lips?

207
00:21:38,297 --> 00:21:40,765
Only when I'm in love.

208
00:21:44,436 --> 00:21:48,167
Patricio Lamumba Beach is only
a 10 minute walk from here--

209
00:21:48,206 --> 00:21:51,232
La Concha is about a mile...

210
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:53,244
This is perfect for you.

211
00:21:53,312 --> 00:21:57,339
